data.description: Adorable 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom home with a fenced yard and 1 car garage. This home is very well maintained and has a good roof, new garage door, Exterior painted in 2019, water heater is 2017, and new windows. Close to restaurants, shopping and the library. come see this lovely home before its gone!! Grant money available for this property. Call for info.
